    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="block clearfix">
    <div class="box">
      <p>예상 관세</p>
      <em>0원</em>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
      <p>예상 부과세</p>
      <em>0원</em>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info_box">
    <span>
      <ul>
        <li>목록통관 $200이하, 일반통관 $150이하 관부가세 면제</li>
      </ul>
    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="block clearfix">
    <div class="box total_box">
      <p>총 예상 구매 가격</p>
      <em>114,000원</em>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info_box">
    <span>* 최종가격 = 제품가격 + 미국 내 배송비 + 세금 + 국제 배송비 + 관부가세</span>
    <span>*</span>
    <span>* 환율은 관세청 고시환율 적용</span>
    <span>* </span>
  </div>



  <% if @hotdeal.h_spare_14.present? %>
    <div class="block clearfix">
      <div class="box">
        <p>Search more by Keyword</p>
        <em><a class="keyword" target="_blank" href="<%= @hotdeal.h_spare_15 %>"><%= @hotdeal.h_spare_14 %></a><i></i></em>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>


</div><!--./info_wrap-->


  <div class="extra_info">
  </div>

  <div class="code_btn">
   <a class="m_btn" target="_blank" href="<%= @hotdeal.h_link %>">Check it out on&ensp;<em>Amazon</em></a>
  </div>

  <%if @hotdeal.h_spare_21.present? %>
    <div class="trix trix-container gradient"><span>About the product</span><p><%= @hotdeal.h_spare_21.html_safe %></p><button class="show-btn fa fa-chevron-down"></button></div>
  <% else %>
    <% if @hotdeal.h_description.present? %>
      <div class="show_des"><p class="description"><%= @hotdeal.h_description %></p></div>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
</div><!--./hotdeal_inner-->



